# Portfolio Core Adherence

Read `agent-context/core-adherence.md` before writing UI.

## Hard rules

- MUST import UI from `@/app/components/` (Button, TextField, TextArea, Select, Link, etc.)
- MUST NOT use raw `<input>`, `<textarea>`, `<select>`, or styled `<button>` in pages/auth/header when LD core exists
- MUST NOT import `lucide-react` in `src/app/pages/`, `src/app/auth/`, `header.tsx`, `footer.tsx`
- MUST use LD `Link` for external `href`; `react-router-dom` `Link` for internal SPA routes only
- MUST run `pnpm run build` from `projects/portfolio/` after UI changes

## Component mapping

| Need | Import |
|------|--------|
| Actions | `@/app/components/Button/Button` |
| Icon actions | `@/app/components/IconButton/IconButton` |
| Text inputs | `@/app/components/TextField/TextField` |
| Multi-line | `@/app/components/TextArea/TextArea` |
| External links | `@/app/components/Link/Link` |
| Icons | `@/app/components/Icons/Icons` |
| Layout | `@/app/components/layout` |

Full inventory and API patterns: `agent-context/core-adherence.md`
